N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 5012.6 - Determination of prizes

State Regulations

For each Take Five game, five winning numbers shall be
randomly selected at a public drawing from a field of 39 numbers from one to
and including 39. Any game panel on the bet ticket having the
following shall be deemed to be a winning game panel: The following shall be the prize categories: The following shall be the percentage of the
winning pool allocated to prize categories: All five winning

First prize
20%
Any four winning

Second prize
30%
Any three winning

Third prize
50%
Any two winning

Fourth prize
0%
